content:
Red beard orchid (Calochilus paludosus) near the Genoa River, VIC - an interesting species with prominent apex tail at the tip of the beard. A handful of plants out here in open grassland - with purple beards (C. robertsonii) also out nearby.

#Orchids #OzPlants #Biodiversity #Ecology #Botany #Photography #Spring #InTheField

content:
I've been thinking a lot about changing my surname too as I really don't like my current one and I don't feel any attachment to it.

I've thought about something Nordic/Viking, as that is part of my cultural heritage (growing up in the part of Britain that was Danelaw centuries ago) but ugh the way that the right has co-opted a lot of Norse stuff is making me conflicted.

content:
The news from Bandcamp is depressing. They sacked about half of staff, including senior editorial staff, and apparently disproportionately targeted union members, of whom they didn‚Äôt have a list. Which suggests that (a) they‚Äôre hiring Pinkertons or someone to identify union sympathisers among staff, and (b) the new management regard those who care about Bandcamp as an institution as a liability, preferring drones who just follow orders.

That cannot possibly bode well for when the owners decide to leverage the attachment that Bandcamp users (both consumers and artists/labels) feel and monetise the hell out of it. The workers who have not been sacked are less likely to push back on, say, plastering the site with unblockable ads or replacing Bandcamp Daily with press releases and LLM-generated pink slime.

I‚Äôll miss Bandcamp a lot more than I missed Twitter.

I write about our #smallholding in North Fife. ‚ÄúOur enemy‚Äù, Mr Andreessen, is people who are pathologically incapable of empathy and taking responsibility for their actions. How many lives is your future built on? I doubt you‚Äôve even considered the answer.

I want many of the same things; a post-scarcity, interplanetary, fully automated sustainable luxury civilisation, but unlike you, I care about who we break along the way, and about who gets left behind.
